{"tid":1667834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律疑難] 競選海報","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:52:43.000Z","uid":274263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"037a5a230f9fe0b3ce6fe2d4936b1fb60e622705","tid":1667834,"uid":274263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"好似聽聞話依家有啲黨派會<span style=\"color: red;\">擅自</span>走去亂Q咁貼自己啲競選海報喺人哋啲舖頭門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果有人又學佢哋咁整啲「支持 光復香港」嘅大貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢哋啲海報就<span style=\"color: red;\">擅自</span>咁逐張幫佢哋加返句競選口號上去會唔會出事架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好驚有人會唔覺意犯咗選舉法呀.... 點算好...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇律師可以解答吓我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57b681f4586719f36376739ba06de89b245c66f","tid":1667834,"uid":318062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"借位唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入黎幫手搞罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667816</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8156c6401d3256a1cbd0f120b32dd13eaee8947a","tid":1667834,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"擅自應該就係無可能<br />\n因為選舉過程中要喺商戶展示競選海報的話<br />\n相關團隊應該要向店主簽同意書以確定同意展示<br />\n我唔記得咗form好似叫<br />\n「在私人物業展示選舉廣告或進行競選活動的批准書」"},{"pid":"7a367490ac68e992e9ca7b6903f16385f2748940","tid":1667834,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"[和理Post] 過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3fc7ce3a\" target=\"_blank